rs is\nsynchrotron emission from electrons accelerated via accretion or merging, the\nmagnetic fields of clusters are generally as small as ~0.1 mu G.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Aug 2001 21:20:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
