 reject pure nu_e->nu_s transitions in favor of nu_e->nu_{mu,tau}\ntransitions only in the Global Analysis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Aug 2001 12:56:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Sep 2001 16:46:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 18 Dec 2001 14:12:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-25"}
